imdb.plot outline: Our world is in a place that needs help. For many, there is something missing inside & a spark that needs ignited to light our internal spirit. Our purpose on this earth is to live a more mindful, conscious life so we can shift the current state we are in. The Prana Warriors mission is to do just that - to open more minds and hearts to the importance of living out of this of space of love, happiness and gratitude - more importantly to give back from the heart. Random acts of kindness and choosing to live a mindful life changes everything. Love is the Prana Warriors mission - because love is the way.
